title: Data Structure
details: Data Structures are the programmatic way of storing data so that data can be used efficiently. Almost every enterprise application uses various types of data structures in one or the other way. This video tutorial will give you a great understanding on Data Structures needed to understand the complexity of enterprise level applications and need of algorithms, and data structures.

title: Modern Javascript
details: Javascript runs the web. It makes your website come alive. If you want to create magic with your websites or web apps, then you need Javascript. Period. In this course, we hope to break down the beginner concepts of the Javascript programming language into manageable parts so you can learn them fast and retain the concepts much longer.

title: HTML5 Crash Course
details: This HTML5 course will be beneficial for all who are looking to start their career in the web development field and aspire to become a Frontend or Full-stack web developer. This HTML course will be the first step toward your goal to become a web developer. We start with exploring HTML Development using some of the most commonly used tags and attributes.

title: Learn Git And GitHub
details: You are going to learn everything that you need to know, to work with Git and GitHub for your day-to-day activities, as a developer, an administrator, a team lead, or anyone, working on software code delivery and management. We are going to dive into the real-life examples just to get practical knowledge of how to manage our source codes, and to have some experience to put in your resume, in case you are looking for employment.

title: Learn ReactJS Quickly
details: React is a javascript library for building UI (User Interface). It is a free and open-source javascript library maintained by Meta (Facebook). Tech giants like Facebook, Netflix, Salesforce, Yahoo, BBC, Airbnb, Asana, Cloudflare, Dropbox, Uber, Tesla, and much more use React for building websites. The main objective of this course is to teach you React in depth from scratch, step by step enabling you to build applications using React.

title: Learn Artificial Intelligence
details: This course is intended for educators, programmers,technicians and students. Artificial intelligence makes it possible for machines to learn from experience, adjust to new inputs and perform human like tasks. Using these technologies, computers can be trained to accomplish specific tasks by processing large amounts of data and recognizing patterns in the data. Artificial Intelligence technology is important as it enables human understanding, reasoning, planning, communication and perception  to be undertaken by software increasingly effectively.
